Privacy Policy for Logop

Last Updated: 02-02-2024

Introduction

Welcome to Logop ("we," "us," or "our"), developed by Prayog Interactive. This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about the types of information we collect, how we use it, and your choices related to your information.

Information We Collect

Unity Ads:

Logop uses Unity Ads to deliver personalized advertisements to users. Unity Ads may collect certain information to provide targeted ads. Please refer to Unity's Privacy Policy for details on the data collected by Unity Ads: https://unity.com/legal/privacy-policy.
Device Information:

We may collect device information, including device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers. This information is used to improve the functionality of the app.
How We Use Your Information

Unity Ads Data:

Data collected by Unity Ads is used to deliver targeted advertisements within the app.
Device Information:

Device information is used to optimize app performance, identify and resolve technical issues, and enhance the user experience.
Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect the information collected against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Your Choices

Unity Ads Preferences:

You may have the option to customize your Unity Ads preferences within the app settings. Refer to the app settings for details.
Opt-Out:

If you do not wish to receive personalized ads, you may have the option to opt-out within the app settings.
Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [your contact email].

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

Acknowledgment

By using Logop, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy.
